summary: Completed comprehensive testing of photo kiosk mobile app with privacy requirements. All backend APIs working correctly, admin PIN protection functional, and privacy requirement verified (receipts don't show customer images).
passed_tests: Backend: All 15 API endpoints working (100% success rate)
Admin PIN verification: Correct PIN (1234) accepted, incorrect PIN rejected
Settings security: admin_pin properly hidden from /api/settings response
Kiosk session creation and QR code generation
Print functionality: Receipt opens without customer images (privacy compliant)
Photo printing: Separate page with 1 photo per page layout
Mobile upload page: Proper mobile UI with file upload interface
Admin modal: PIN gate working correctly before admin access
